            "body": "Your second screenshot doesn't show a virtual line, so this is a \"tea and no tea\" request.\n\nWhat you seem to be asking for is for the virtual _text_ handler to put virtual text on _different_ lines if there is free room. This looks nice but almost impossible to do correctly and robustly, and most certainly outside of the complexity budget for this feature in core. May be possible for a plugin, though.",
